This is a list, based on functionality, of the macros which have an alternate _d name, representing a reentry into the BOOST_PP_WHILE looping construct:

arithmetic
  • BOOST_PP_ADD_D
  • BOOST_PP_DIV_D
  • BOOST_PP_MOD_D
  • BOOST_PP_MUL_D
  • BOOST_PP_SUB_D
array
  • BOOST_PP_ARRAY_INSERT_D
  • BOOST_PP_ARRAY_REMOVE_D
  • BOOST_PP_ARRAY_REPLACE_D
comparison
  • BOOST_PP_EQUAL_D
  • BOOST_PP_GREATER_D
  • BOOST_PP_GREATER_EQUAL_D
  • BOOST_PP_LESS_D
  • BOOST_PP_LESS_EQUAL_D
  • BOOST_PP_NOT_EQUAL_D
control
  • BOOST_PP_DEDUCE_D
list
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_APPEND_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_AT_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_CAT_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_FILTER_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_FIRST_N_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_FOLD_LEFT_d
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_FOLD_RIGHT_d
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_REST_N_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_REVERSE_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_SIZE_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_TO_ARRAY_D
  • BOOST_PP_LIST_TRANSFORM_D
selection
  • BOOST_PP_MAX_D
  • BOOST_PP_MIN_D
repetition
  • BOOST_PP_REPEAT_FROM_TO_D
  • BOOST_PP_REPEAT_FROM_TO_D_z
tuple
  • BOOST_PP_TUPLE_INSERT_D
  • BOOST_PP_TUPLE_REMOVE_D
  • BOOST_PP_TUPLE_REPLACE_D
base
  • BOOST_PP_WHILE_D
